<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Maintenance Scheduled - 12done.com</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5; }
    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4F46E5; }
    .content { padding: 30px 0; }
    .scheduled-badge { background: #8B5CF6; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .calendar-box { background: #F5F3FF; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #8B5CF6; }
    .calendar-date { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #5B21B6; }
    .calendar-time { font-size: 18px; color: #7C3AED; margin-top: 5px; }
    .details-box { background: #FAF5FF; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #8B5CF6; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #E9D5FF; }
    .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .detail-label { color: #6B21A8; font-weight: 500; }
    .detail-value { color: #581C87; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #666; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">12done.com</div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="scheduled-badge">Maintenance Scheduled</div>

    <h1>Your maintenance visit has been scheduled!</h1>

    <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

    <p>The maintenance work for your request has been scheduled. Please ensure someone is available at the property during the scheduled time.</p>

    <div class="calendar-box">
      <div class="calendar-date">{{scheduledDate}}</div>
      <div class="calendar-time">{{scheduledTimeSlot}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="details-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Request Details</h3>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Property</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{propertyTitle}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Issue</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{title}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Important:</strong> Please ensure access to the property is available during the scheduled time slot. If you need to reschedule, please contact your landlord as soon as possible.</p>

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View Request Details</a>
    </p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The 12done.com Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} 12done.com. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This is a transactional email regarding property maintenance on 12done.com.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
